    "Though, there is also research on video-based solutions for cases where physical positioning systems are unavailable.",
    "There are three main approaches to pose estimation: (1) Visual Odometry (VO), (2) visual Simultaneous Localization and Mapping (vSLAM) and (3) Structure from Motion (SfM), all of which share common components (Taketomi et al. 2017).",
